also happy new year from Taiwan! Thanks for all of the love and support over the past year. 2022 was full of a lot of extreme ups and downs for me. I hope 2023 is kind to all of us, and I can’t wait to share more gentle chaos with you all in the new year 💕

I wrote a book! :,)

 I’ve been working on “Gentle Chaos” since 2021 and I poured so much of my tender gay heart into the poems, essays, and artwork in this book. 

I’m having a hard time wrapping my head around the idea that all my little thoughts and words will be in book stores soon and that people will be able to take this little piece of me home with them and keep it on their bookshelves. My heart is so full ♥️

Not only is there a book ~ but there’s also a companion Guided Journal and Oracle Deck! It all comes out on my birthday October 3rd but you can preorder your copy TODAY! (available anywhere you buy books!)
